**7.6 THE 2.72 GPA PERFORMANCE LIMIT:**
THE SOFTWARE IS DESIGNED TO BE **PRAGMATICALLY FUNCTIONAL**. IF THE SOFTWARE PERFORMS AT A LEVEL CONSISTENT WITH A 2.72 GPA, IT IS OPERATING WITHIN ITS DESIGNED PARAMETERS. NO REFUNDS OR CODE REVISIONS WILL BE GRANTED FOR "NOT BEING A 4.0."
